<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-517-298  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 517 298.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  June 5 1990 v4 n21 p4(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Coastal Associates Publishing L.P. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>PosterWorks gives users a preview. (S.H. Pierce andamp; Co. PosterWorks2.0) (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Said, Carolyn.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   S.H. Pierce and Co. (product introduction).andO;Product:   PosterWorks 2.0 (Presentation software) (product introduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionGraphics SoftwareColor.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>EPS support, layout capabilities addedandM;By Carolyn SaidandM;Cambridge, Mass.andP;  -- People who need jumbo-sized printouts will gain moreoptions while generating them with Version 2.0 of PosterWorks, a program thatallows printing of color images up to 100 square feet on any color PostScriptdevice.andM;The upgrade, scheduled for July shipment, adds layout and composition toolsto PosterWorks, according to its developer, S.H.andP;  Pierce andamp; Co.andM;Previously, users enlarged files for printing via a dialog box but could notview the actual documents on screen.andP;  With Version 2.0, users see fileson-screen.andP;  Layouts can be assembled by importing separate files, which areon separate layers and can be resized, cropped and moved.andM;&quot;With the new version's preview capabilities, you can actually lay outwhatever you import on a pasteboard setup and get a more intuitive feel forwhat it will look like,&quot; said beta-user Ed Vigil, a technical illustrator atthe Los Alamos National Laboratory in New Mexico.andM;PosterWorks, which already could import Mac-generated TIFF files, as well asimages from Scitex, Crosfield and Hell scanners, now also can importEncapsulated PostScript files.andM;&quot;Being able to use EPS as well as TIFF files is a real nice capability,&quot;Vigil said.andP;  &quot;Now we can take images from Adobe Illustrator and turn theminto posters.&quot;andM;A new plug-in module lets designers create custom halftone screens for adocument or each element.andP;  Each plate of a four-color separation can beprinted with a unique dot shape, angle and frequency.andM;Like the previous version, PosterWorks 2.0 includes color calibration tools.andO;The program can output documents as a single page but more commonly tilesthem, providing automatic crop and registration marks, page numbers, andbleeds for quick assembly.andM;Before the original PosterWorks came out last year, Vigil said, he hadattempted on his own to enlarge files to compose a poster.andP;  &quot;But I had to gothrough too many iterations.andP;  PosterWorks takes all the guesswork out.&quot;andM;PosterWorks 2.0 will be priced at $295.andP;  Users of the original version, whichsold for $167, will receive free upgrades.andM;S.H.andP;  Pierce andamp; Co. is located at 1 Kendall Square, Suite 323, Building 600,Cambridge, Mass.andP;  02139; (617) 395-8350.andO;</TEXT></DOC>